data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED and offering $5000 towards closing costs or rate buy down and a ONE YEAR WARRANTY with a full price offer!!! Check out this adorable starter home!! Don't let the age fool you, this home is almost completely updated! The backyard is something to see for yourself, it's huge, with so much potential! Not to mention fenced in, has raised garden boxes, and an apple tree.. A concrete slab with a fire pit, easily accessed from the two car garage and sliding doors in the dining room! Such a convenient location as well, close to everything American Legion has to offer! Don't let this one get away!
